      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you're saying i should take an extra dose? im kinda confused, wont that mess up my levels? i thought i was supposed to be careful with lithium. if the nausea is just a side effect, how much extra should i actually take to feel better? i dont want to end up in the hospital lol",
